Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma's house
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.89,0:01:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天会有什么好东西在等着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What wonders await me today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.52,0:01:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新鲜现烤的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh-baked cookies?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.60,0:01:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Story time?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.92,0:01:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每一针都充满爱的毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sweater with love in every stitch?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.85,0:01:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还等什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I waiting for?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.97,0:01:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.22,0:01:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.30,0:01:26.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进来坐一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:26.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in and sit for a while
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.87,0:01:29.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃饼干  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:29.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a cookie, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.20,0:01:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶  你做的饼干是全海洋最棒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma, you make the best cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the deep blue sea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.66,0:01:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma's cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁想要舔勺子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, who wants to lick the spoon?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, me, me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我们一路开回了家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then we drove all the way home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关车窗  在这大冷天里飞驰着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with all the windows down in the freezing cold
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.27,0:01:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再跟我讲个我小时候的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me another story about when I was a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.05,0:02:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三点了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,3:00
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上班要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be late for work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来坐我的车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hop in my car
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我送你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll drop you off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:09.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(748,388)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Grandma
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916,784)}入口
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你忘了要亲亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you forgot your kissy-kissy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure did
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.24,0:02:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你送我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ride
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.90,0:02:28.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:28.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家今天的心情真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's in a good mood today
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很想过来煞风景  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love bursting your bubble, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.98,0:02:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们这是在笑你  不是在跟你笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're laughing at you, not with you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做了什么可笑的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I do something funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你额头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your forehead
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我额头可笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My forehead is funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶的小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, grandma's boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲亲亲亲亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kissy-kissy-kissy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.23,0:02:52.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:52.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被奶奶亲没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:53.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's nothing wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with getting kisses from your grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.45,0:03:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你是个穿纸尿裤的巨婴就更对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,especially if you're a big baby who wears diapers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还吸大拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, and sucks his thumb
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩布娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and plays with dolls
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, um
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿着长得让脚都伸不出的睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wears pajamas with feet in them
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还带着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and carries his, um
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小毯毯到处跑  还
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,binky around, and, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right already
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,振作点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道还有个喜欢你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know someone who still likes you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.07,0:03:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真知道吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.30,0:03:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.40,0:03:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不要在大庭广众之下受辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have been publicly humiliated for the last time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为你之前的事情难过  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that happened to you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我认识的最大人的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the most adult person I know
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要知道奶奶都是些什么货色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know how grandmas are
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她们爱小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They love babies
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.52,0:04:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不能在她身边表现得像个小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just can't act like a baby around her
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么时候没对过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have I ever not been right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是男子汉了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a man now, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是时候该表现得像个男子汉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's time you started acting like one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不太确定要怎么表现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure I know how
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来演示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to demonstrate
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  挺起胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, puff out your chest
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在说  免除税款
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now say "tax exemption”
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免除税款
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tax exemption
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你必须学会品味自由爵士乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you must acquire a taste for free-form jazz
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.00,0:04:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.92,0:04:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ready
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要跟你奶奶说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to tell Grandma?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a grown-up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对此不准有任何异议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No ifs, ands or buts about it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,男子汉要做男子汉要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A man's got to do what a man's got to do
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你就到她身后  我来推一把
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then you get behind her and I'll push
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这可不在计划内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, we didn't say that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就只缺成年礼蛋糕上的糖霜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All we need now is the icing on the maturity cake
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好几年来我一直在养着这些小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been growing these babies for years
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,络腮胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sideburns
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多么惊喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a nice surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来吧  让奶奶给你亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here, give your granny her kissy-kissy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Grandmother
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再亲下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the kissing has to stop
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样跟她说  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell her like it is, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要搞幼稚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more baby stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对  祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is right, Grandmother
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲亲是给小宝宝的  而我不再是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kisses are for babies, which I am no longer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have grown up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.95,0:05:40.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是自然之道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:40.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is nature's way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对极了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are absolutely right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.04,0:05:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  我说得当然对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, of course I am
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.70,0:05:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这绝对再也不会被当成小宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will definitely not be treated
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like a baby around here ever again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.05,0:05:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴你从我的角度看问题  祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am glad you see it my way, Grandmother
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我很高兴看到事情办妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad that's settled
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我又要怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what am I going to do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些新鲜现烤的饼干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with all these fresh-baked cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Grandmother
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们大人是不摄取甜食的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We adults don't partake in the consumption of sweets
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.20,0:06:08.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  派
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:08.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.42,0:06:09.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:09.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多来点  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep 'em coming, Granny
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不搞幼稚这套不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So much for no more baby stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.58,0:06:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了戴吃饼干专用帽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't forget the cookie-eating hat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那顶吃饼干专用帽是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my cookie-eating hat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  是我小时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, it was when I was a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看谁来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, look who's here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的老大人孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my big old adult grandson
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.16,0:06:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祖母  我要和派大星来场成熟的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, I need to have a mature conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with Mr. Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.92,0:06:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.75,0:06:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warm milk
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:46.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,700)}我爱奶奶
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.00,0:06:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,围兜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bib
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你额头上的是不是唇印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that a kissy mark on your forehead?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该是要当大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are supposed to be adults
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃饱了不要打闹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No roughhousing with a full tummy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's the baby?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the baby
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当大人也太没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being grownup is boring
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱当小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love being a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我也听不懂爵士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't get jazz
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.87,0:07:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都快为你感到难过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost feel sorry for you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.07,0:07:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,困在穿尿布的尴尬时期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trapped in the awkward phase of diaper days
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无法理解当大人收获的丰厚回报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never to know the rich rewards of being a grownup
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.35,0:07:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一批新鲜现烤的饼干来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a fresh batch of cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回报是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rewards, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, there's
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想  我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, we, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们听了爵士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we went over the jazz
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶  我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma, I'm full
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有饼干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的午餐时间也到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It appears to be my lunch hour
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大人也必须吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grownups have to eat, too
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能吃这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess this will have to do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不想吃这小宝宝吃的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't want this baby food
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一大块的蒸珊瑚怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a big piece of steamed coral?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.00,0:08:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太营养了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nutritious
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Story time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.72,0:08:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Story time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Story time?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会喜欢的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll enjoy this Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.07,0:08:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这精彩的故事讲的是一只神奇的海妖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful story about a magical sea leprechaun
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你肯定没兴趣听这宝宝书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you wouldn't be interested in this babybook
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是关于常规保养的技术手册
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the technical manual
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on Routine Active Maintenance
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.62,0:08:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,引人入胜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fascinating
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有插图  我就喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No pictures, just the way I like it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小指指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wittle finger
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别乱动  别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold still, hold still
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了点没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All better?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.87,0:08:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorta
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根指头也有点疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This finger hurts a little bit, too
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要我送你礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about I give you a present?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  希望是饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I hope it's cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another hat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对派大星  这是毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick, it's a sweater
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每一针都充满了爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With love in every stitch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我难道就没有礼物吗  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't I get a present, Grandma?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你办公用品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's some office supplies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没做包装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't wrap them
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定不会介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,3:00
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大人该去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for adults to go to work
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜拜  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定想睡午觉是不是  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you would fancy a nap, huh, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还没走吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're still here, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在还不急着走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have to leave yet
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班迟到也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can be late for work
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.94,0:09:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那样才不是大人做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't be the adult thing to do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.30,0:09:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll be going
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.18,0:09:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有好多大人的公务要干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,got a lot of adult-type business to take care of
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.78,0:10:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.20,0:10:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你顺路来看我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for stopping by, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, that is it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有空的话要再回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come again if you get the chance
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进入冷酷的大人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out into the cold grown-up world
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.17,0:10:13.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:13.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,alone
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without a sweater
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toodle-oo
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道我何时才能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know when I'll be back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你可忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how busy you are
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's asleep
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.25,0:10:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想长大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to grow up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想吃饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有喝奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And milky
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要每一针都充满爱的毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a sweater with love in the stitches
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想穿纸尿裤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to wear didies
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想骑小车车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to ride in my wagon
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想抱抱毛绒玩具小先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to cuddle-wuddle with Mr. Stuffykins
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.62,0:10:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想坐上海马马摇啊摇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to rocky-rock on my seahorsey
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.09,0:10:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还想要亲亲我的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I want kissy-kissy on my boo-boo
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不必依靠变成小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来得到奶奶的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get Old Grandma's love
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你长得有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter how grownup you get
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一直都会是我的小小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will always be my Little Baby Boo
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.28,0:11:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记好了  你亲亲奶奶的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And remember, you can kiss your Grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也是可以当大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and still be an adult
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶  问下能不能别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma, could you not mention
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟蟹堡王那些人说这事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this to the guys down at The Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:27.05,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(237,346)}章鱼村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,408)\frz19}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:31.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(412,716)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(358,272)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(288,348)\frz22.06}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz22.06\pos(476,674)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看  我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, look, I got my
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.84,0:12:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.42,0:12:52.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚还以为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a second I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你买的鼓风机跟我的一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got the same reef-blower as me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag, you're it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:09.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,452)}吹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:09.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786,912)}吸
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你让我家干净到发亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you made my house sparkly clean
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure did
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没让章鱼哥也今天开心一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We haven't improved Squidward's day yet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来搞他家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do his house
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on out here?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在玩新买的鼓风机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're playing with our new reef-blowers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.95,0:13:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩鼓风机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Playing with a reef-blower?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.09,0:13:39.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我听过最幼稚的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:39.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is the most childish thing I've ever heard of
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.85,0:13:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是很好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's fun
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.33,0:13:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩个特大号头发烘干机怎么好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could playing with one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,oversized hair dryers possibly be fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.75,0:13:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chafed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:54.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(716,920)}擦 伤
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来整你家吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do your house, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你在冒气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're steaming
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.44,0:14:09.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟蒸菜似的  只是聪明点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:09.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're like a steamed vegetable, only smarter
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我窗户放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put my windows back
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们挺你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're on your side
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随时都能成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any second now
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.00,0:14:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这是最后底线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, this is the final straw
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要搬到很远的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am going to move so far away
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远到我可以吹的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I will be able to brag about it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.33,0:14:33.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:33.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宁愿把我脑干扒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would rather tear out my brain stem
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它带到最近的十字路口正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,carry it into the middle of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the nearest four-way intersection
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再拿着它跳绳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and skip rope with it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不住我现在住的这破地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than go on living where I do now
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是最后底线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this the final straw?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要搬到很远的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to move so far away
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远到你可以吹的地步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you can brag about it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你宁愿把你脑干扒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you rather tear out your brain stem
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走到最近的丁字路口正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,walk out into the middle of the nearest three-way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.25,0:14:58.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是十字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:58.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four-way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十字路口正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four-way intersection
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再拿着它跳绳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and skip rope with it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不继续住你现在住的破地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than continue living where you do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就搬来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then move to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我讨厌这个频道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate this channel
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼村
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tentacle Acres
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.69,0:15:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这里  快乐离你只有一吸盘之遥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where happiness is just a suction cup away
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:16.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(438,312)}章鱼村
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, can I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来这享乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here about the happiness
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在要搬进来住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be moving in now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.87,0:15:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己一个来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.27,0:15:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人跟着我一起来  对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's nobody with me, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宁静祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peace and quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.22,0:15:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在或曾经是海绵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you now or have you ever been a sponge?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.10,0:15:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么还
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about a
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  不是海星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no starfish
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只是个普通正常爱宁静的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a regular, normal peace-loving
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,466)}杏仁糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,814)}小心
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算到天堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heaven at last
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.40,0:16:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在养老院里见过的人机灵多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:16:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've seen more alert people in a retirement home
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无脑生活研讨会要往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which way to the Living Without a Brain seminar?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be late
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火鸡三明治都比你会还嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've heard better comebacks from a turkey sandwich
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(420,920)}笨 蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找点正经事做去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a life
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方比我预想的还要好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is better than I expected
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,302
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,302
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,303
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,303
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后304
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and 304
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且一个菠萝都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And not a pineapple in sight
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Clary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.14,0:16:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天我们就要开启新生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow we begin life anew
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新生活街304号  我是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,304 New Life Street, Squidward speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是不会再搬回去的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no way I am moving back there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.80,0:16:47.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我总算跟我同类住在一块了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:47.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am finally among my own kind
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.57,0:17:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我要骑自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll take my bike today
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的事情我做主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm my own man
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些邻居深谙生活之道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, these neighbors know how to live
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,216)}满溢健康
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,细致入微
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Intensive
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们肯定没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet they won't have
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.32,0:17:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They have it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(762,344)}罐装面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,738)}切完片\N就是好东西
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罐装面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Canned bread
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这城好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This town is great
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肯定会被惊艳到  如果这地方有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would really be impressed if it had
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(504,482)}形意舞学院
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,形意舞学院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an interpretive dance academy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,组团跳舞可更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's even better in a group
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这城好完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This town is perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竖笛三重奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A clarinet trio?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another great day
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, look
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家今天都在骑车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's on their bike today
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(926,204)}满溢健康
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生活变得越来越好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It just gets better and better
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All together
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sort of
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点不想吹竖笛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't feel like playing my clarinet today
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.22,0:18:56.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:56.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, this is great
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.18,0:19:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们怕是得把这城改名叫章鱼哥天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They might as well rename this town
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's Paradise
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.52,0:19:02.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者可能应该改
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:02.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过分的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too Much Paradise
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(776,602)}随时回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536,556)}吸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(592,820)}吹
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,落叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(712,918)}走 开
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清理落叶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just getting the leaves
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能小点声  铁肺物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you pipe down over there, Iron Lung?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子每当找乐子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like when it comes to having fun
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就站不住脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you don't have a leg to stand on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.02,0:20:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not funny
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.85,0:20:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on over here?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在玩鼓风机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's playing with a reef-blower
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.15,0:20:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Playing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼓风机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With a reef-blower?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.32,0:20:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我听过最幼稚的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the most childish thing I've ever heard of
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是很好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's fun
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.04,0:20:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩个特大号头发烘干机怎么好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you possibly have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with one of those oversized hair dryers?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.95,0:21:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快还来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.87,0:21:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag, you're it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(856,200)}咖啡厅
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能给你点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I get you boys?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你瞅啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那俩鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:37.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,216)}章鱼村
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.07,0:21:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.45,0:21:37.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要说服章鱼哥回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we've just got to convince
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:37.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward to come back home
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.70,0:21:38.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你带道歉蛋糕了没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:38.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got our apology cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,562)}对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.57,0:21:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ready
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  请问有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, can I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能点一份一号餐  特大份的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get a large number one, extra size?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.57,0:21:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你刚已经吃了三份炸牡蛎壳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you just ate three orders of fried oyster skins
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.90,0:21:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱炸牡蛎壳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love fried oyster skins
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:01.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1112,484)}大门关闭
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.82,0:22:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  你们这类人不得进入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:22:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, but your kind isn't allowed here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.85,0:22:03.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不走  奥维尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:03.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not leaving, Orville
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你警棍备好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got your nightstick ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炸牡蛎壳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fried oyster skins?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,140)}大门关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:09.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,140)}大门开启
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.67,0:22:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能进去点餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we got to order inside
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.82,0:22:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位看着很像章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looked like Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.21,0:22:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位看着很也像章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looked like Squidward also
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.70,0:22:27.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是成了暴民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:27.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in angry mob form
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站在那别动  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都退后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.02,0:22:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手上有园艺工具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got gardening tools
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, just read this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.02,0:22:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经过深思熟虑精心编排的投诉清单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A well thought-out and organized list of complaints
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.30,0:22:48.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看  是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:48.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, look, it's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.48,0:22:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We finally found you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.23,0:22:52.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:52.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.55,0:22:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是章鱼哥了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:22:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you Squidward now?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.25,0:22:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:22:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grievances?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.21,0:23:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这座城属实让人委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This town is a grievance
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.00,0:23:02.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要有项法律
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:02.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There should be a law
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.12,0:23:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,禁止让这么多装小气自大狂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,against so many stuck-up tightwads
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.01,0:23:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都住在同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,living in one place
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.32,0:23:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这座城需要被毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This city needs to be destroyed
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.47,0:23:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最起码也要重新粉刷成别的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or at least painted a different color
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.78,0:23:15.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提醒你  你没必要住在这知道不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:15.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,FYI, you don't have to live here, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.70,0:23:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.77,0:23:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm leaving ASAP
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.60,0:23:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是章鱼哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.65,0:23:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.02,0:23:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是章鱼哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.07,0:23:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.93,0:23:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是章鱼哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.27,0:23:28.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行吧  你慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:28.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay, take your time
